summary: Clean well defined female bodies with nice fingernails.
descriptionHtml:
These textures are clean and the bodies remain well defined and feminine. They also have nicer looking fingernails.
 
This contains no esp, so just drag the texture folder and drop to your games Data folder.

As always, my mods are open for use by others without further permission.

>>>>>>>>>>
Many thanks to Bethsoft for an excellent game. Hope to thank them soon for a CS.

Thanks to Darkone for providing a home for modders and downloaders.
author: Bond
